c32e0460-0275-4fa3-8039-d2a0eb2ab845.title: <player>
c32e0460-0275-4fa3-8039-d2a0eb2ab845.text: I'm in search of a quest.

67a816f1-10ef-4245-8603-80bc2c6dd05c.title: Man
67a816f1-10ef-4245-8603-80bc2c6dd05c.text: I'm sorry I can't help you there.

bf2838e3-f3cb-4a3a-ae49-f0d7d0ebef08.title: Man
bf2838e3-f3cb-4a3a-ae49-f0d7d0ebef08.text: Get out of my way, I'm in a hurry!

adbb34d5-3344-4b65-9155-0346396b2ae6.title: Man
adbb34d5-3344-4b65-9155-0346396b2ae6.text: Hello there! Nice weather we've been having.

options.text: I'm in search of a quest.
I'm in search of enemies to kill.

ad9a0f4b-7a03-41d4-af85-f75ecf112eef.title: Man
ad9a0f4b-7a03-41d4-af85-f75ecf112eef.text:
No, I have nothing I wish to get rid of. If you want to
do some trading, there are plenty of shops and market
stalls around though.

17f62895-d365-48bc-9bd5-83cf3f0fc1e4.title: Man
17f62895-d365-48bc-9bd5-83cf3f0fc1e4.text:
I'm a little worried - I've heard there's lots of people
going about, killing citizens at random.

e8ebf0db-d6a0-4a02-9670-3e931da7704b.title: <player>
e8ebf0db-d6a0-4a02-9670-3e931da7704b.text: I'm in search of enemies to kill.

758c6adc-a5cb-4779-bbac-fb5bda254639.title: Man
758c6adc-a5cb-4779-bbac-fb5bda254639.text:
I've heard there are many fearsome creatures that
dwell under the ground...

cf05faa6-68c7-4b4d-9445-c2920e96abf4.title: Man
cf05faa6-68c7-4b4d-9445-c2920e96abf4.text:
Not too bad, but I'm a little worried about the increase
of goblins these days.

252610eb-6706-427d-ba97-7b71c8cd7711.title: Man
252610eb-6706-427d-ba97-7b71c8cd7711.text: No, I don't want to buy anything!

60cb8568-1637-4817-b370-d761c4344a96.title: Note
60cb8568-1637-4817-b370-d761c4344a96.text:
You will be able to talk to, attack and pickpocket these NPCs.
Left click attack, right click talk to and shift right click pickpocket.
